item.title: Watching Black Panther
item.description: After a significant wait I was finally able to watch Black Panther: Wakanda Forever. It is a long movie so I had to digest it in two sittings but it was well worth the time. I will try to avoid discussing specific plot points but if you haven’t seen the film yet then you may want to wait to read this until later. I am always impressed by Winston Duke’s acting skills.
